Each Unveiled Beauty: Cultivating YOU event has had its own powerful messages and last Friday, May 12, Annie Meehan and Char Dobbs touched the hearts of our attendees with their personal journeys and their messages. They got real. They shared themselves and they raised us up!

THANK YOU to all those brave women who came out on Friday night! And thank you also to Miss Char Dobbs for reminding our attendees that regardless of our size we deserve to feel beautiful & confident in styles that represent our most authentic self! Thank you to Miss Annie Meehan for her powerful words and embracing us with the words, "You are ENOUGH". In reality, we are MORE than enough! Lastly, thanks to Amber Rose Bjerke for hosting yet another a great event.
